divs: Sighting DetailsI was watching t.v. when my sister and mom returned home and came inside and told me that aliens were outside. I then preceded to walk outside and look at them. They were four lights that looked like a blank projection on the clouds and they just went in a pattern. At first I believed that it was just spotlights but than my sister said they had moved from a nearby city called Marysville, and I also heard about other reports and decided it was indeed a alien craft or some type of military test. I decided to stop watching and later in the evening when I came out it was gone.
Summary: Four oval lgihts on the sky doing wierd patterns.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Browns Valley
